{"tid":2082445,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家近來都好乖 搭黨鐵 比足車費拍卡入閘","createTime":"2020-06-28T04:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T04:59:27.000Z","uid":321771,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8fbd647af3cdf80347affbce677b7123d9f0dbba","tid":2082445,"uid":321771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"近日香港人都好好，甚少見到人<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">跳閘/推閘</span></span></strong>坐黨鐵。<br />\n亦冇乜聽到<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>廢老卡</strong></span></span>嘅嘟聲，相信會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">罷鐵</span></strong></span>嘅人一定已經習慣咗用其他交通工具代替。<br />\n<br />\n香港人都好大方，相信都<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">原諒咗</span></span>黨鐵一切<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罔顧人命</span></span></strong></strong>嘅作為。<br />\n<br />\n近日越來越黨鐵職員查飛，本人相當讚揚管治有效！<br />\n發覺好多學生哥都俾人捉過<br />\n可能佢哋冇錢交罰款，所以<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">客戶服務中心</span></strong></strong></span>長期出現<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大量神沙</span></span></strong><br />\n提提大家<br />\n<strong>根據香港法律第 454 章的硬幣條例</strong>就列明，「以面額不少於 $1 的硬幣而言，所支付的款額不超逾 $100」；「以面額少於 $1 的硬幣而言，所支付的款額不超逾 $2」。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">換句話說，1 元、2 元、5 元、10 元大銀，只要合共不超過 $100 就可以使用；而 1 毫、2 毫、5 毫，只要合共不超過 $2 就可以使用。</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">增值，唱錢買飛都係！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後溫馨提示<br />\n港鐵是你家，坐車有乜頭暈身㷫，記得<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">㩒鐘搵車長求助</span></span></strong>"}]}